[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m**Benefits of proper setup:**[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Precise brand recognition** across different contexts and spellings[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Competitive intelligence** that filters out competitor noise[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Market context** that focuses on your operational regions[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Positioning** that aligns monitoring with your business model[m
